Immortal Rain (メテオ・メトセラ, Meteor Methuselah) is a shōjo manga created by Kaori Ozaki. It was first published in the Japanese monthly anthology Wings as Meteor Methuselah. As of September 2007, the current eight volumes have been published in English by Tokyopop, with the rest of the series, when published in Japan, expected to follow. The 10th volume has recently been released in Japan. It's published in French by Doki-Doki.